# ============================================================
# TRANCHI AI — Environment Variables
# Total cost to run: $0/month (use free tiers below)
# ============================================================

# ── DATABASE — FREE ──────────────────────────────────────────
# supabase.com → New project → Project Settings → API
# Free tier: 500MB, unlimited API calls
SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=your_service_role_key_here

# ── AI / LLM — FREE ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Pick ONE. Both are completely free, no credit card needed.
#
# OPTION A (recommended): Groq — fastest, best JSON output
#   1. Go to console.groq.com
#   2. Sign up (no credit card)
#   3. API Keys → Create → copy it here
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# OPTION B: Google Gemini — 1M tokens/day free
#   1. Go to aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#   2. Sign in with Google → Create API key
#   3. Copy it here
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...

# OPTION C: Anthropic — paid fallback (only if you have a key)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── EMAIL — FREE ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Gmail SMTP. No Twilio needed to start.
# Setup: myaccount.google.com → Security → 2-Step Verification
#        → App passwords → Select app: Mail → Generate
EMAIL_ADDRESS=your@gmail.com
EMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
REPLY_TO_EMAIL=your@gmail.com

# ── OPTIONAL: GOOGLE MEET AUTO-BOOKING ───────────────────────
# Only needed for auto-booking meetings when buyers reply YES.
# Skip this on day 1 — system flags interested buyers for manual callback.
# Setup: console.cloud.google.com → Calendar API → Service Account → JSON key
# GOOGLE_CREDENTIALS_FILE=google_credentials.json
YOUR_EMAIL=your@gmail.com
YOUR_TIMEZONE=America/Chicago

# ── OPTIONAL: SMS (add when you get a Twilio number) ─────────
# System uses email-only until these are set.
# Requires A2P 10DLC registration before sending marketing SMS.
# TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token
# TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER=+1XXXXXXXXXX

# ── ZERO-COST HOSTING ────────────────────────────────────────
# For the seller funnel (/sell page) to be live 24/7:
#
# Option A — Render.com free tier:
#   render.com → New Web Service → connect GitHub → Root: tranchi-ai
#   Add env vars above → Deploy
#   Keep alive: use uptimerobot.com (free) to ping /health every 5 min
#
# Option B — Run deal-hunt locally on demand (no hosting needed):
#   python main.py deal-hunt
#   Schedule with Windows Task Scheduler or Mac/Linux cron
